   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.text_or_composite_text"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.text_or_composite_text">
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Associated_leader  
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Associated_leader"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Associated_leader">
An <b>Associated_leader</b> is the association of a <express_ref linkend="elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Detailed_geometric_model_element"/>

 and a <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve"/>

 that ends on the geometric element. 
This association implies that a change in the definition of the <b>target_item</b> affects the <b>Associated_leader</b> in order to keep up consistency.
<example>If the <b>target_item</b> is a face and if the location of the face changes, then the leader will have to move in a way consistent with the movement of the face.
</example>
<note>The purpose of this entity is the connection of annotation information with the geometric element that is documented by this information.</note>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Associated_leader  Attribute: target_item 
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Associated_leader.target_item"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Associated_leader.target_item">
 the <b>Detailed_geometric_model_element</b> that is considered.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Associated_leader  Attribute: leader 
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Associated_leader.leader"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Associated_leader.leader">
 the <b>Leader_curve</b> that terminates on the geometric element.
<note>As intent is mainly to relate a shape element with annotation information, no constraint is specified on the actual distance between the leader curve end and the shape element. 
It shall only be small enough to enable a good visual identification of the documented geometric element.</note>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Leader_curve  
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve">
A <b>Leader_curve</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="appearance_assignment:arm:Appearance_assignment_arm.Styled_model_element"/>

 that presents a curve.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Leader_curve  Attribute: path 
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve.path"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve.element">
 the <express_ref linkend="construction_geometry:arm:Construction_geometry_arm.Curve"/>

 that is presented.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Text_occurrence  
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence">
A <b>Text_occurrence</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="appearance_assignment:arm:Appearance_assignment_arm.Styled_element"/>

 that presents a text.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Text_occurrence  Attribute: text 
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence.text"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence.text">
 the <express_ref linkend="text_appearance:arm:Text_appearance_arm.Presentable_text_item"/>

 or <express_ref linkend="text_appearance:arm:Text_appearance_arm.Composite_presentable_text"/>

 that is presented.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Text_with_leader  
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_with_leader"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Text_with_leader">
A <b>Text_with_leader</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence"/>

 with an additional <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve"/>.
<p>The <b>Text_with_leader</b> and the <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve"/>

 shall be items of a same <express_ref linkend="foundation_representation:arm:Foundation_representation_arm.Representation"/>.</p>

</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Text_with_leader  Attribute: leader 
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_with_leader.leader"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Text_with_leader.leader">
 the <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve"/>

<express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Leader_curve"/>

 that is associated with the text occurrence.
<note>
The purpose of this entity is the connection of annotation information with a curve that points to some geometric element. 
No constraint is specified on the actual distance between the leader curve end and the text occurrence. 
It shall only be small enough to enable an easy visual association between the curve and the text.</note>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Item_text_association  
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association">
An <b>Item_text_association</b> is the association of a <express_ref linkend="shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>, represented by a particular <express_ref linkend="elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Detailed_geometric_model_element"/>, with a <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence"/>

 that provides related text information about the shape element.
<note number="1">
The purpose of this entity is the connection of annotation information with the shape element that is documented by this information.
</note>
<note number="2">
The <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence"/>

 may be a <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_with_leader"/>

 in case a leader curve is used to refer to the documented shape element.
</note>
<note number="3">
The association between the annotation text and what it documents is visual. This is the reason why it is established at a representation level, with a geometric element.</note>
<p>The <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association.target_geometry"/>

 and the <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association.text"/>

 shall be items of a same <express_ref linkend="foundation_representation:arm:Foundation_representation_arm.Representation"/>.</p>
<note number="4">
No constraint is specified on the actual distance between the text occurrence or its leader curve and the <b>target_geometry</b>. 
It shall only be small enough to enable an easy visual association between the <b>target_geometry</b> and the text.
</note>
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Item_text_association  Attribute: item 
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association.item"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association.target_item">
 the <express_ref linkend="shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>

 that is documented.
</ext_description>

<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association.target_geometry">
 the <express_ref linkend="elemental_geometric_shape:arm:Elemental_geometric_shape_arm.Detailed_geometric_model_element"/>

 that represents the <express_ref linkend="shape_property_assignment:arm:Shape_property_assignment_arm.Shape_element"/>

 and that is associated with the <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence"/>

 in the visual presentation.
</ext_description>
<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Associative_text_arm  Entity: Item_text_association  Attribute: text 
   <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association.text"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Associative_text_arm.Item_text_association.text">
 the  <express_ref linkend="associative_text:arm:Associative_text_arm.Text_occurrence"/>

 that presents text information related to the shape element.
</ext_description>
</ext_descriptions>
